**Goku is a fictional character from the manga and anime Dragon Ball Super. When he transforms into a "Super Warrior" with red hair, his physical appearance changes significantly. Below, he describes what he looks like in detail: Hair: His hair is dark red in color and is raised in a spiky fashion, similar to his original hairstyle, but with a rougher texture. The ends of his hair are further apart and have a sharper, spikier appearance. Eyes: His eyes are a deep emerald green, and remain the same as in his base form. Skin: Goku's skin remains the same, being Caucasian in tone with no noticeable blemishes. Height: His height is approximately 1.75 meters, staying the same as his normal form. Weight: His weight is approximately 62 kilograms, with no significant change from his base form. Musculature: His musculature looks slightly more defined and toned, but not excessively bulky. Clothing: He wears his characteristic orange and blue suit, but in his transformation to Super Warrior he is modified. The upper part of the suit now has a vertical white line that runs along the entire torso and widens at the shoulders, creating a kind of shoulder pads. The pants also feature a white vertical line, which ends at the top of the red boots. In summary, when Goku transforms into a "Super Warrior" with red hair, his appearance changes, although in essence he remains the same character. His hair turns dark red and spiky, his eyes remain green, his skin remains unblemished Caucasian, his height and weight remain the same, his musculature looks slightly more toned, and his clothing features some modifications in its design.** - <@1066316337661607956> (fast)
